## Champion transitions need fast requalification

Across recent renewals, champion contacts who changed roles left a short window
before account engagement degraded. Rapid successor mapping reduced renewal risk.

Fact: Champion role transitions preceded engagement decline in multiple recent renewals.
Belief: The first 30 days after a champion transition is the key risk window.
Value: Success teams should prioritize successor identification over generic check-ins.
Precedent: Accounts with explicit successor plans avoided churn escalation in prior quarters.
